import React from 'react'
import { Button, Col, Container, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap";

const SearchBar = ({books, setBooks}) => {
    return (
      <Container className="mt-5">
        <Row>
          <Col sm={12}>
            <Form className="d-flex">
              <Form.Control
                type="search"
                placeholder="Search"
                className="me-2"
                aria-label="Search"
              />
              <Button>
                Search
              </Button>
            </Form>
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    );
  }

export default SearchBar
